channel.title: [PI] Making new rank
channel.description:
Using Final Jugment soruce (erasedpkz base)
First I want to replace the "Donator" Rank, with my costum rank "BetaTester" (BT)
I was told that I needed to replace all the Donator thing on :Player.java & PlayerSave.java, I did that and appeared me a bunch of erros of other .java files like "Cannot find "Donator" and stuff like that, and in the following files I change from "donator" to "BT" (betatester):
[code]ActionHandler.java ClickingButtons.java Client.java CombatAssistant.java Commands.java ItemAssistant.java Player.java PlayerSave.java[/code]
After compiling it actually I don't get 18 or more errors but I do get 2 errors, here they are:
[IMG]http://i887.photobucket.com/albums/ac77/Caldito/donortobt.png[/img]
In ItemAssistant, I don't know whats wrong... But in Client.java I search for "Donator", but theres no Donator word...
I'll be wating for an answer, Thank You!
-Heinz

no dude… the compiler is saying that the symbol c.isDnator = 1; in madturnip.connection.java cannot be found in client.java, and is saying the same for itemassistant.java, it cannot find the symbol because it has to be declared in itemassistant.java and client.java
